%e A317614 For n = 1 the matrix M(1) is
%e A317614   1
%e A317614 with trace Tr(M(1)) = a(1) = 1.
%e A317614 For n = 2 the matrix M(2) is
%e A317614   1, 2
%e A317614   4, 3
%e A317614 with Tr(M(2)) = a(2) = 4.
%e A317614 For n = 3 the matrix M(3) is
%e A317614   1, 2, 3
%e A317614   6, 5, 4
%e A317614   7, 8, 9
%e A317614 with Tr(M(3)) = a(3) = 15.
